    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, how is the clot risk lower with a lower dose? i thought warfarin was to stop clots. if i take less, wouldn't that make clotting more likely? you sound really sure about this though, so i'm a bit confused. should i just go ahead and start the 2mg twice a day tomorrow then?",
